lass=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-12 grvsc-t9ljLd-1\">element</span><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-1 grvsc-t9ljLd-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-12 grvsc-t9ljLd-1\">innerHTML</span><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-1 grvsc-t9ljLd-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-1 grvsc-t9ljLd-7\">+=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-1 grvsc-t9ljLd-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-8 grvsc-t9ljLd-11\">&#39;&lt;h2&gt;Hello World!&lt;/h2&gt;&#39;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>innerHTML로 가져온 내용이 <code>&#x26;</code> <code>&#x3C;</code> <code>></code>를 포함하는 경우 각각 <code>&#x26;amp;</code>과 <code>&#x26;lt;</code> <code>&#x26;gt;</code>로 대체됩니다.</p>\n<p>innerHTML을 사용하여 삽입한 태그는 HTML 태그로 파싱 되기 때문에 HTML5에서는 innerHTML로 삽입된 <code>&#x3C;script></code> 태그가 실행되지 않도록 지정하고 있습니다. 또한, 보안 점검에서 innerHTML이 사용된 경우 거부되기도 합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-htmlelementinnertext\" style=\"position:relative;\">2. HTMLElement.innerText<a href=\"#2-htmlelementinnertext\" aria-label=\"2 htmlelementinnertext permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>MDN Docs: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/innerText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/innerText</a></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container dark-default-dark grvsc-ps-t9ljLd\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tlfloc-3 grvsc-t9ljLd